dct_title_s: Geologic map of the San Diams and Ontario quadrangles, Los Angeles and San Bernardino counties, California
dct_alternative_sm: DF-91 Geology San Diams - Ontario quadrangle
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle SAN DIMAS, CA 1981, ONTARIO, CA 1981, NIMA 2452 IV SE - Series V895."
"Prepared in cooperation with the Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
